REQUIREMENTS:
• College/ University degree, major in hospitality or sales/ marketing is preferable
• At least from 3 to 4 years of experience onwards in sales and marketing for Assistant Sales Manager and 5 years onward for Sales Manager, and knowledge on F & B is an advantage
• Female candidate is preferred
• Good verbal and written communication in both English and Vietnamese
• Passionate, doable spirit, result-based approach and highly responsible, proactive at work
• Good leadership skills and analyzed mind
• Experience in B2B sales

BENEFITS:
